y are '''family''' movies.}}\n#: {{ux|en|This is a '''family''' restaurant, stop making out!}}\n# {{lb|en|gay slang}} [[homosexual|Homosexual]].\n#: {{ux|en|I knew he was '''family''' when I first met him.}}\n\n====Translations====\n{{trans-top|suitable for children and adults}}\n{{multitrans|data=\n* Bulgarian: {{tt+|bg|семе́ен}}\n* Finnish: {{tt|fi|[[perhe]]-}}\n* German: {{tt|de|Familien-}}\n* Maltese: {{tt|mt|familja|f}}, {{tt|mt|familji|p}}\n* Polish: {{tt+|pl|rodzinny|m}}, {{qualifier|family movie}} {{tt+|pl|familijny|m}}\n* Portuguese: {{tt+|pt|de família}}\n* Russian: {{tt+|ru|семейный}}\n* Slovak: {{tt|sk|rodinný}}\n{{trans-bottom}}\n\n{{trans-top|(slang) homosexual}}\n* Catalan: {{tt+|ca|marieta|m}}\n* Finnish: {{tt+|fi|homppeli}} {{q|informal}}, {{tt+|fi|fägäri}} {{q|slang}}\n* German: {{tt|de|vom anderen Ufer}}\n* Norwegian: {{tt+|no|skeiv}}\n* Swedish: {{tt+|sv|bög}}\n}}<!-- close {{multitrans}} -->\n{{trans-bottom}}\n\n===See also===\n* [[:Category:Family]]\n* {{sense|taxonomy, rank}}\n:* {{l|en|domain}}\n:* {{l|en|kingdom}}\n:* {{l|en|phylum}}/{{l|en|division}}\n:* {{l|en|class}}\n:* {{l|en|order}}\n:* {{l|en|superfamily}}\n:* '''family'''\n:** {{l|en|subfamily}}, {{l|en|tribe}}\n:* {{l|en|genus}}\n:* {{l|en|species}}\n\n===References===\n* {{R:OneLook}}\n* {{R:Merriam-Webster Online}}\n* {{R:Dictionary.com}}\n* {{R:Keywords 21st}}\n* {{R:Keywords|page=1}}\n* {{R:Century 1911}}\n* {{R:Webster 1913}}\n\n===Further reading===\n* {{pedia}}\n* {{pedia|Family (disambiguation)}}\n* {{pedia|Family of sets}}\n* {{pedia|Family (biology)}}\n* {{R:Greens|id=h5wwtha|sense=1|pos=n}}\n\n{{cln|en|2-syllable words|collective nouns}}\n{{C|en|Collectives|Family|Family members|LGBTQ}}"}}